15
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,320
That has its own particular laws.

16
00:00:44,940 --> 00:00:47,150
Those laws are different than

17
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:49,360
an electrically charged particle moving in

18
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,300
the field of a magnet.

19
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:53,700
They're different than,

20
00:00:53,700 --> 00:00:56,060
you know,

21
00:00:56,060 --> 00:00:59,420
there are specific laws of nature.

22
