Then there's a more general framework.

23
00:01:04,090 --> 00:01:06,880
What are the rules for the allowable laws?

24
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:10,240
Are there rules for the allowable laws?

25
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:12,860
What's the grand framework in which

26
00:01:12,860 --> 00:01:15,220
all of the various different specific laws

27
00:01:16,050 --> 00:01:17,140
are framed in?

28
00:01:18,679 --> 00:01:20,480
And the second,

29
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:22,100
it's really the second question

30
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:23,720
which we're really interested in.

31
00:01:24,090 --> 00:01:26,460
The first question will provide us with illustrations.

32
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:29,540
Illustrations of the principle of motion.

33
