1941
01:06:02,480 --> 01:06:04,060
And in fact,

1942
01:06:04,060 --> 01:06:07,280
the magnitude of the vector r

1943
01:06:07,710 --> 01:06:10,780
is the radial distance from the origin to the particle.

1944
01:06:10,780 --> 01:06:11,560
That is true.

1945
01:06:11,560 --> 01:06:12,340
r,

1946
01:06:12,340 --> 01:06:13,340
presumably...I

