1999
01:07:50,320 --> 01:07:50,880
x,

2000
01:07:50,880 --> 01:07:51,720
y,

2001
01:07:51,720 --> 01:07:52,300
and z.

2002
01:07:52,300 --> 01:07:55,780
What about the velocity of a particle?

2003
01:07:55,780 --> 01:07:58,080
The velocity of a particle is also

2004
01:07:58,080 --> 01:07:58,760
